\c 17 Mambo weAsiria anokunda Samaria nokutapa vaIsiraeri 17 1 Zvino negore regumi namaviri raAhazi mambo waJudha, Ho‑ shea mwanakomana waEra wakatanga kubata ushe hwaIsiraeri paSamaria, akahubata makore mapfumbamwe. 2 Akaita zvakaipa pamberi paJehovha; asi haana kufanana namadzimambo aIsiraeri akamutangira. 3 Zvino Sharimaneseri mambo weAsiria akasvika kuzorwa naye, Hoshea akava muranda wake, akamuterera mutero. 4 Asi mambo weAsiria wakati achiona kuti Hoshea akarangana navamwe kumumukira, nokuti wakanga atuma nhume kuna Soromoni mambo weIjipiti, akarega kuterera mambo weAsiria mutero sezvaaiita gore rimwe nerimwe, mambo weAsiria akamupfigira mutorongo akamusunga. 5 Ipapo mambo weAsiria akafamba nenyika yose, akaenda Samaria, akarikomba makore matatu. 6 Negore repfumbamwe raHoshea, mambo weAsiria akakunda Samaria, akatapa vaIsiraeri, akaenda navo Asiria, akavaisa paHara, napaHabhori, parwizi Gozani, napamaguta avaMedhi. 7 Izvozvo zvakaitwa, nokuti vana veI‑ siraeri vakatadzira Jehovha Mwari wavo, iye wakanga avabudisa panyika yebipiti kwavakanga vakabatwa naFarao mambo vakatya vamwe vamwari, 8 va‑ kafamba nemitemo yendudzi dzakanga dzadzingwa naJehovha pamberi pavana veIsiraeri, neyamadzimambo eIsiraeri ya‑ vakatema ivo. 9 Vana veIsiraeri vakaita pakavanda zvisina kururama pamberi pa‑ Jehovha Mwari wavo, vakazvivakira ma‑ tunhu akakwirira mumaguta avo ose, kubva pachirindo chavarindi kusvikira pamaguta akakombwa. 10 Vakazvimutsira shongwe namatanda okunamata nawo pamatunhu ose akakwirira, napasi pemiti yose mitema. 11 Vakapisirapo zvinonhuwira pamatunhu ose akakwirira, sezvaiita ndudzi dzakanga dzabviswa pamberi pavo naJehovha; vakaita zvakashata zvakatsamwisa Jehovha; 12 vakashumira zvifananidzo, zvavakanga vanzi naJehovha, "Regai kuita chinhu ichi." 13 Kunyange zvakadaro Jehovha wakapupurira Isiraeri naJudha nemiromo yavaporofita vose navawoni vose, akati, "Dzokai panzira dzenyu dzakaipa, muchengete mirairo yangu nezvandakatema, sezvakarehwa nomurayiro wangu wose wandakaraira madzibaba enyu, wandakatuma nemiromo yavaporofita varanda vangu." 14 Kunyange zvakadaro, vakaramba kuteerera, vakawomesa mitsipa yavo, semitsipa yamadzibaba avo, vakanga vasingatendi Jehovha Mwari wavo. 15 Vakaramba mitemo yake nesungano yake yaakaita namadzibaba avo, nezvipupuriro zvake zvaakavapupurira, vakatevera zvisina maturo, ivo vakava vasina maturo, vakatevera ndudzi dzakavapoteredza, ivo vavakanga varairwa naJehovha kuti varege kuita saivo. 16 Vakasiya mirairo yose yaJehovha Mwari wavo, vakazviitira zvifananidzo zvakaumbwa, zvemhuru mbiri; vakaitawo matanda okunamata nawo, vakanamata hondo yose yokudenga, vakashumira Bhaari. 17 Vakapinza vanakomana navakunda vavo mumoto, vakauka nokuita uroyi hwavo, vakazvitengesa kuti vaite zvakaipa pamberi paJehovha, vakamutsamwisa. 18 Naizvozvo Jehovha wakatsamwira vaIsiraeri kwazvo, akavabvisa pachiso chake; hakuna vakasiyiwa, asi rudzi rwaJudha bedzi. 19 Kunyange navaJudhawo havana kuchengeta mirairo yaJehovha Mwari wavo, asi vakafamba nemit000 yavaIsiraeri, yavakatema. 20 Jehovha akarasha vana veIsiraeri vose, akavatambudza, akavapa mumaoko avaparadzi, kusvikira avarashira kure nechiso chake. 21 Nokuti wakabvarura vaIsiraeri paimba yaDhavhidhi; vakaita Jerobhoamu mwanakomana waNebhati, mambo wavo, Jerobhoamu akatsautsa vaIsiraeri, vakarega kutevera Jehovha, akavatadzisa
